Package: ezPurrr
Title: Make Purrr Easier To Use.
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Wanjia", "Guo", , "wanjiag@uoregon.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: ezPurrr is a facilitating package for `Purrr`. It has straightforward `sample` functions to sampling from a nested data set. It can also easily `broadcast` a written function to all other rows of the data set. 
